Build dependencies
==================

* LIBJPEG (optional)
* CURL
* LIBRT (required if --enable-multiprocess is given)
* EXPAT (required if if --enable-components is given)
* FFMPEG
  + libavcodec
  + libavdevice
  + libavformat
  + libavutil
  + libswresample
  + libswscale
* SDL2
* SDL2_image
* SDL2_ttf
* XERCES-C
